Articles.Content: The staging area of the editor doesn't even show 0 m/s, it shows nothing at all for DeltaV. And the engines won't fire on the pad either. PLAZ HALP.

You’re going to need to include more information, for example:

  • KSP version;
  • Mod list;
  • Screenshot(s) of the problem, both in the VAB and on the launchpad;
  • Log files.

If you’re using RO/RP-1 then you need to make sure you’re using the right type of fuel tank- the early Aerobee engine is pressure fed and so requires high pressure fuel tanks or the engine won’t work. Check that you have the right fuel in the tanks too. Try installing MechJeb and using the delta-V readout from that, it’s more accurate than the stock one for RP-1.
